### What I learned

Has I keep learning about grid, I learned that this properties are important to plan your layout 


```css
.item {
   grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            grid-template-areas:
            "daniel daniel jonathan kira"
            "jeanette patrick patrick kira";
}
```

```


